@startuml Arena Selection State Diagram
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor LightBlue
  BorderColor Black
  ArrowColor Black
}

title Arena Selection State Machine

[*] --> InProgress: startArenaSelection()

state InProgress {
  [*] --> WaitingForElimination: Arena selection started
  WaitingForElimination --> WaitingForElimination: eliminateArena()\n(Player 1 eliminates)
  WaitingForElimination --> WaitingForElimination: eliminateArena()\n(Player 2 eliminates)
  WaitingForElimination --> CheckingCompletion: Arena eliminated
  CheckingCompletion --> WaitingForElimination: Multiple arenas remain
  CheckingCompletion --> Completed: One arena remains
}

InProgress --> Completed: Only one arena remains\n(auto-select)

Completed --> [*]: Arena selected

note right of InProgress
  **State:** InProgress
  **Actions:**
  - Players eliminate arenas
  - Real-time updates
  - State stored in Redis
end note

note right of Completed
  **State:** Completed
  **Actions:**
  - Arena auto-selected
  - Proceed to weapon selection
end note

@enduml

